b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":2469,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Gala Dragalia Remix Is Coming Soon!","message":"<div>Gala Dragalia Remix starts on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1631512800\\"><\/span>!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0What Are Gala Dragalia and Gala Dragalia Remix?<\/div><div>The initial appearance rate for 5\\u2605 adventurers and dragons will be boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%! If you get a 5\\u2605 summon or 5\\u2605 featured summon, the appearance rate will return to the initial 6%.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><span style=\\"color: rgb(226, 80, 65);\\">The newly added 5\\u2605 adventurers Undercover Grace (flame) and Farren (light) will also appear in subsequent summon showcases.<\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div><span style=\\"color: rgb(226, 80, 65);\\">Adventurers added in past Gala Dragalia summon showcases may appear in this summon showcase as well. For information about which adventurers may appear, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Appearance Rates and check the Appearance Rates section.<\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25bcNewly added featured adventurers:<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Undercover Grace (flame\/sword)<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Farren (light\/dagger)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25bcFeatured adventurer from past Gala Dragalia summon showcases:<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Gala Mascula (water\/blade)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25bcFeatured dragon from past Gala Dragalia summon showcases:<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Gala Thor (light)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Gala Dragalia Remix event duration:<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1631512800\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1631858399\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Get a closer look at the featured adventurers and dragon below.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Featured adventurers:<\/div><div>\\n<div class=\\"summonPickUp\\"